<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-73-0096 </DOCNO><TEXT>The principal characteristics of dosimetry and narrow X-ray beams(4Mv)monitoring are investigated for use in estereotatic radiosurgery. Anadditional collimator system and a estereotatic system (Leksell type)are presented. Dosimetric parameters like tissue-air ratio, peak scatterfactor, isodose curves are studied. (M.A.C.).</TEXT></DOC>